FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781887672
OL,3,CThree inmates found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering child killer
OL,6,FNone of the defendants answered
OL,7,Fquestions in their police interviews,
OL,8,For gave evidence during the trial.
OL,9,FThey will be sentenced on Friday 19
OL,10,FJune.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
